<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1911-09-21T17:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1911-09-21T17:00:00-05:00" n="424" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d424">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 818.00/231b</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                Minister <persName type="to">Leavell</persName>
                            </hi><note n="5" xml:id="d424fn5">Same to the American Legations at
                                Tegucigalpa, Managua, San Salvador.</note>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-09-21T17:00:00-05:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">September 21, 1911—5 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Department’s February 9, 3 p.m. Inform Government to which you are
                            accredited that the United States desires it clearly understood that she
                            has not recognized Tinoco’s Government in Costa Rica and would not
                            regard his recognition by Government to which you are accredited as
                            evidence of a friendly feeling toward the United States.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>